---
import * as ExternalLinks from '@/enums/external-links.enum.js'
import * as Routes from '@/enums/routes.enum.js'
import Html from '@/layouts/Html2/index.astro'
import AppBar from '@/layouts/AppBar/index.astro'
import Splash from '@/layouts/Splash2/index.astro'
import Article from '@/layouts/Article/index.astro'
import BottomBar from '@/layouts/BottomBar/index.astro'
import converPicture from '@/assets/images/about_page.jpg'

export const prerender = true
---

<Html
	title="About Us • Redmerah"
	description="Welcome to Redmerah, your one-stop for becoming a productivity powerhouse. We're more than just a platform; we're your partner in streamlining your workflow and conquering your to-do list. Ever feel overwhelmed by a overflowing task list? Redmerah can help. With the right tools at your fingertips, you can tackle any project with confidence.">
	<Splash>
		<svg width="512" height="512" viewBox="0 0 512 512" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
			<g clip-path="url(#clip0_864_188)">
				<path d="M256 320V240C256 222.327 241.673 208 224 208C206.327 208 192 222.327 192 240V464C192 478.91 192 486.365 189.564 492.246C186.316 500.087 180.087 506.316 172.246 509.564C166.365 512 158.91 512 144 512V512C129.09 512 121.635 512 115.754 509.564C107.913 506.316 101.684 500.087 98.4359 492.246C96 486.365 96 478.91 96 464V240C96 169.308 153.308 112 224 112C294.692 112 352 169.308 352 240V320C352 343.016 352.037 357.876 352.812 369.25C353.559 380.194 354.829 384.378 355.656 386.375C360.528 398.131 369.869 407.472 381.625 412.344C383.622 413.171 387.806 414.441 398.75 415.188C399.166 415.216 399.586 415.243 400.011 415.27C416.056 416.266 424.079 416.764 429.607 419.361C437.289 422.97 442.625 428.648 445.75 436.538C448 442.216 448 449.478 448 464V464C448 479.086 448 486.63 445.427 492.653C442.092 500.457 435.2 507.05 427.256 510.035C421.125 512.339 414.085 512.026 400.006 511.402C397.324 511.283 394.728 511.14 392.219 510.969C376.39 509.889 360.548 507.509 344.906 501.031C309.622 486.416 281.584 458.378 266.969 423.094C260.491 407.452 258.111 391.61 257.031 375.781C255.981 360.383 256 341.703 256 320Z" fill="url(#paint0_linear_864_188)"/>
				<rect x="32" y="32" width="448" height="288" rx="64" fill="#7A0000" stroke="#FF1414" stroke-width="64"/>
			</g>
			<defs>
				<linearGradient id="paint0_linear_864_188" x1="288" y1="288" x2="288" y2="512" gradientUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
					<stop stop-color="#A30000"/>
					<stop offset="1" stop-color="#FF1414"/>
				</linearGradient>
				<clipPath id="clip0_864_188">
					<rect width="512" height="512" fill="white"/>
				</clipPath>
			</defs>
		</svg>
	</Splash>
	<AppBar route={Routes.About} />
	<Article
		disabledAuthor
		title="About Redmerah"
		subtitle="Built for getting things done and make productivity painless."
		coverPictureUrl={converPicture.src}>
		<p>Welcome to Redmerah, your one-stop for becoming a productivity powerhouse. We're more than just a platform; we're your partner in streamlining your workflow and conquering your to-do list. Ever feel overwhelmed by a overflowing task list? Redmerah can help. With the right tools at your fingertips, you can tackle any project with confidence.</p>
		<section>
			<h2 id="Supercharged-by-Innovation"><a href="#Supercharged-by-Innovation">Supercharged by Innovation</a></h2>
			<p>Redmerah stays ahead of the curve by harnessing the latest web technologies. This translates to applications that run smoothly and offer robust features, whether you're conquering tasks online or working offline.  Stuck on a plane with no Wi-Fi? No problem! Redmerah keeps your data readily available, even without an internet connection. We understand that reliable connectivity isn't always a guarantee, and that's why we prioritize flexibility. With Redmerah, you can work seamlessly even in remote locations, ensuring your productivity never takes a backseat.</p>
			<p>Speaking of data, we prioritize your privacy. Unlike other platforms that hoard your information like digital dragons guarding their treasure, Redmerah applications save everything locally on your device. This means your settings, history, and all your important data remain under your control. You decide what stays and what goes. Redmerah empowers you to be the master of your digital domain.</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2 id="Designed-for-You-by-Humans"><a href="#Designed-for-You-by-Humans">Designed for You, by Humans</a></h2>
			<p>We're obsessed with crafting user interfaces (UI) and user experiences (UX) that are a joy to use. Our applications are meticulously designed to adapt seamlessly to any device you choose, be it a desktop computer, a tablet, or your trusty smartphone. We believe that productivity shouldn't be a chore. Our interfaces are intuitive and aesthetically pleasing, making it a pleasure to organize your tasks and conquer your goals. No matter your tech savviness, Redmerah's user-friendly design makes it easy to get started and maximize your efficiency</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2 id="Focus-on-What-Matters"><a href="#Focus-on-What-Matters">Focus on What Matters</a></h2>
			<p>Unlike other platforms that bombard you with ads, turning your screen into a chaotic marketplace, Redmerah is a distraction-free zone. We prioritize functionality over flashy banners or intrusive pop-ups. Here, you can concentrate on getting things done without the annoyance of constant interruptions</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2 id="Fueling-the-Future"><a href="#Fueling-the-Future">Fueling the Future</a></h2>
			<p>Redmerah is a passionate project driven by the support of amazing people like you. We operate on donations and sponsorships, and if you find our tools valuable, we encourage you to consider becoming a sponsor. Reach out to us at <a href={"mailto:" + ExternalLinks.ContactEmail}>{ExternalLinks.ContactEmail}</a> or donate us <a href={ExternalLinks.Donate}>here</a>. Every contribution fuels our passion to develop even more useful applications that empower you to achieve more.</p>
		</section>
		<section>
			<h2 id="Your-Voice-Shapes-Our-Journey"><a href="#Your-Voice-Shapes-Our-Journey">Your Voice Shapes Our Journey</a></h2>
			<p>Have an idea for a feature? Encountered a bug? We&#39;re all ears! Contact us at <a href={"mailto:" + ExternalLinks.ContactEmail}>{ExternalLinks.ContactEmail}</a>, and we&#39;ll listen. Your feedback is the cornerstone of our development process, and it helps us create tools that truly meet your needs.</p>
			<p>Thank you for joining the Redmerah community! We're thrilled to have you on board as we embark on this journey to unlock your full potential.</p>
		</section>
	</Article>
	<BottomBar />
</Html>
